      • usePrefillService

        boolean usePrefillService()
        Configuration to either use input data as argument and use prefill service defined on IC or ignore prefill service provided in IC and use complete input as actual data. If false then use use input as actual data and ignore prefill service, true then use prefill service defined on IC and use input as arguments. By default its false.
        Returns:
        whether to use prefill service or not
